import { Container ,Header, Product, ProductList, ProductName, ProductDescription, ProductPrice, ChatInput, ChatSubmit, Chat, ChatInputWrapper, ChatBox, BubbleBot, BubbleUser } from './styled'
import data from './data.json'
import ProductData from './product.json'
import {useState, useEffect} from 'react'

function App() {
  const [productList, setProductList] = useState([])

  useEffect(() => {
    setProductList(ProductData.product)
  }, [])

  console.log(productList);
  return (
    <Container>
      <Header>Toko Cuy</Header>
      {/* Product */}
      <Product>
        {productList.map((product, index) => {
          return(
            <ProductList>
        <ProductName>{product.name}</ProductName>
        <ProductDescription>{product.description}</ProductDescription>
        <ProductPrice>Rp. {product.price}</ProductPrice>
        </ProductList>
          )
        })}
      {/* <ProductList>
        <ProductName>T-sirt</ProductName>
        <ProductDescription>Lorem Ipsum Doler Ipsum</ProductDescription>
        <ProductPrice>Rp.300.000</ProductPrice>
        </ProductList>
      <ProductList>
        <ProductName>Meja</ProductName>
        <ProductDescription>Lorem Ipsum Doler Ipsum </ProductDescription>
        <ProductPrice>Rp.500.000</ProductPrice>
        </ProductList>
      <ProductList>
        <ProductName>Makanan</ProductName>
        <ProductDescription>Lorem Ipsum Doler Ipsum</ProductDescription>
        <ProductPrice>Rp.100.000</ProductPrice>
        </ProductList> */}
      </Product>

      <Chat>
          <ChatBox>
            <BubbleBot>ChatBot</BubbleBot>
            <BubbleUser>ChatBot</BubbleUser>
            <BubbleBot>ChatBot</BubbleBot>
            <BubbleUser>ChatBot</BubbleUser>
            <BubbleBot>ChatBot</BubbleBot>
            <BubbleUser>ChatBot</BubbleUser>
            <BubbleBot>ChatBot</BubbleBot>
            <BubbleUser>ChatBot</BubbleUser>
            <BubbleBot>ChatBot</BubbleBot>
            <BubbleUser>ChatBot</BubbleUser>
            <BubbleBot>ChatBot</BubbleBot>
            <BubbleUser>ChatBot</BubbleUser>
          </ChatBox>
        <ChatInputWrapper>
        <ChatInput></ChatInput>
        <ChatSubmit>Submit</ChatSubmit>
        </ChatInputWrapper>
      </Chat>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default App;
